{
  "stem": "27351.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They spent a night in jail, apparently, where they tortured by the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course they had arms with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had pistols and, and grenades.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Were they-- did they have to dig their own grave?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know, and I'll never know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somehow I never stopped mourning my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know why I feel differently with the death of my father and the death of my mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this young life-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he was 19.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was going to be 20 in one month.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my mother was insane the first few hours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had problems calming her down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I kept telling her, no-- [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] --it was not him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe it was not him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She gradually calmed down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She had to live for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we never talked about it anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this is another thing that I regret, because she must have known more about how they were actually discovered.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There are two versions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One is that at least-- a little Jewish boy who was hidden actually in the bunker, somewhere around there, went out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was spotted by S men-- SS men coming by.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they started to--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--beat him up, and tell us where-- who's here, and where are you, and where is your mother, and is there anybody else around here.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he gave them up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is one version.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Another version that I read in some books-- but it's all hearsay.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody knows exactly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Another version was that perhaps they did draw in apparently-- they did draw in some group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this group of partisans didn't quite trust them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they told them, well, all right, you're going.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
